DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

90-2533. Cleveland Bar Assn. v. Nardi.

On motion to receive objection as filed instanter. Motion for leave to file instanter granted. Sua sponte, relator granted leave pursuant to Gov. Bar R. V(21) to file answer brief. Pursuant to Gov. Bar R. V(22), this cause is to be set for argument.

Holmes, J., not participating.
